November 21, 1968. No. 1065,

Mise.

Valenti v. Lumbard, Chief Judge, U. S. District Court, et al. John Manning Regan on the motion. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General of New York, and Jean M. Coon, Assistant Attorney General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus dismissed pursuant to Rule 60 of the Rules of this Court.
